satisfied by our local operations there, placement of direct work or vendor orders for supplies, opportunities to bid on
supply contracts, transfer of technology or other forms of assistance. However, in certain cases, our commitments may
be satisfied through other parties (such as our vendors) who purchase supplies from our non-U.S. customers. In certain
