Increase to Revenue $137 $559 $394
Increase/(decrease) to Earnings from Operations ($190) $250 ($263)
Increase/(decrease) to Diluted EPS ($0.29) $0.34 ($0.36)
Significant adjustments during the three years ended December 31, 2018 included reach-forward losses of $736, $445
