on the T-X Trainer and $291 on the MQ-25 Stingray.
During the second quarter of 2018, we recorded a charge of $148 related to the outcome of the Spirit litigation,
including the write-off of $137 of receivables.
We increased our quarterly dividend from $1.42 to $1.71 in December 2017 and to $2.06 in December 2018.
