from February 2008 to August 2009; Vice President and General Manager of
Combat Systems from May 2006 to February 2008; and Vice President and
Program Manager for Future Combat Systems. Mr. Muilenburg also serves on
the board of Caterpillar Inc.
Jenette E. Ramos 53 Senior Vice President, Manufacturing, Supply Chain & Operations since April
2018. Ms. Ramos joined Boeing in 1988, and her previous positions include
Senior Vice President, Supply Chain and Operations from June 2017 to April
2018; Vice President and General Manager, BCA Fabrication from April 2014 to
May 2017; Vice President, Supply Chain Management from January 2012 to
